Introduction
============

Leolo is a RSS/Atom feed manager library. It allows you to:

- Add/Edit a list of feeds.
- Get any content from feeds:
    - Feed title.
    - Feed url.
    - Feed's last update.
    - Feed's new entries:
        - Entry title.
        - Entry link.
        - Entry content.
        - Entry enclosures.
        - Entry links (included in content).
- Filter new entries.

Requirements
============

- Python 2.6
- SQLAlchemy
- Pyparsing
- Feedparser (http://www.feedparser.org/)

Installation
============

Just execute:
``python setup.py install``

